In our documentation [page|http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DOC/Confluence+Search+Syntax]:

bq. Confluence will ignore common words like "the" unless you place your query within quotes.

This is untrue, as "the" is part of the stop words. Same goes to "IT", "it", etc. Even though these stop words are placed within quotes, Confluence will ignore them.

