Users editing in Rich text view are experiencing "cursor bounce" every time a draft is autosaved. (The cursor jumps all the way to the top of the page.) We have our draft save frequency set to 30 seconds since we have users working on detailed documentation and we do not want to take any chances on losing their work.  We have discussed setting it to a more lengthy time period to make it less annoying but this is not a feasible option given the nature of the work that could be lost. We desire to have cursor position maintained in order to allow people to work in rich text mode without interruption while not having to risk any lost work product.  The best solution would be to have this fixed please.

